{"id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0003","text":"旁人常在笑我堅持","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["單戀","不被理解","堅持"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["旁人","笑","堅持"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,0,0,2,4,5,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["pong4","jan4","soeng4","zoi6","siu3","ngo5","gin1","ci4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"旁人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"常","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"在","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"笑","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"堅持","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「旁人常在笑我堅持」描寫了外界對「我」的單戀行為的不理解和嘲笑，增加了角色的孤獨感。"},"source":{"title":"牆紙","artists":["容祖兒"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_738","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0004","text":"我只得堅持","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":5},"semantics":{"themes":["堅持","無奈"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["只得","堅持"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,9,3,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","zi2","dak1","gin1","ci4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"只得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"堅持","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「我只得堅持」簡潔有力，表達了在外界壓力下，除了堅持別無選擇的無奈感。"},"source":{"title":"牆紙","artists":["容祖兒"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_738","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0005","text":"我喜歡堅持","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":5},"semantics":{"themes":["堅持","喜愛"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["喜歡","堅持"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,9,3,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","hei2","fun1","gin1","ci4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"喜歡","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"堅持","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「我喜歡堅持」語氣轉為正面，強調了對這種單戀行為的某種程度的認同或享受，與上一句的無奈形成對比。"},"source":{"title":"牆紙","artists":["容祖兒"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_738","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0006","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0006","text":"即使只相隔着塊紙","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["單戀","距離","阻礙"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["即使","相隔","紙"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,9,4,2,4,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zik1","si2","zi2","gaak3","zoek6","faai3","zi2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"即使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"只","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"相隔","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"塊","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"紙","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「即使只相隔着塊紙」以「紙」比喻兩人之間看似微小卻無法跨越的隔閡，點明了單戀的物理或心理距離。"},"source":{"title":"牆紙","artists":["容祖兒"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_738","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0007","text":"相親必須同時同意","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["關係","同意"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["相親","同意"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,0,0,0,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["can1","bit1","seoi1","tung4","si4","tung4","ji3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"相親","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"必須","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"同時","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"同意","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「相親必須同時同意」是歌詞中一個較為突兀的句子，可能隱喻雙方關係的建立需要共同意願，但在此語境下顯得有些不合邏輯，或許是為了強調「我」的單方面付出與對方無關。"},"source":{"title":"牆紙","artists":["容祖兒"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_738","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0008","text":"地上最遠的只怕是 同場","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["距離","疏遠"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["最遠","只怕","同場"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,5,3,9,4,2,0,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["dei6","zeoi3","jyun5","dik1","zi2","paa3","si6","tung4","coeng4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"地上","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"最遠","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"只怕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"同場","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"「地上最遠的只怕是 同場」運用反諷，指出即使身處同一場合，心理上的距離也可能比天涯海角更遠，強調了對方對「我」的忽視。"},"source":{"title":"牆紙","artists":["容祖兒"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_738","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0009","text":"也不看我一次","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["被忽視","失落"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["不看","一次"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,3,4,5,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jaa5","bat1","hon3","ngo5","jat1","ci3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"看","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一次","pos":"NUM"}],"syntax_notes":"「也不看我一次」直接表達了被對方完全忽視的失落感，與上一句的「同場」呼應。"},"source":{"title":"牆紙","artists":["容祖兒"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_738","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0010","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0010","text":"牆紙一般貼在門牆是我","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["自我定位","附屬","無存在感"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["牆紙","貼","門牆","我"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,3,3,4,2,0,0,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["coeng4","zi2","jat1","bun1","tip3","zoi6","mun4","coeng4","si6","ngo5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"牆紙","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"一般","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"貼","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"門牆","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"}],"syntax_notes":"「牆紙一般貼在門牆是我」將自己比喻為牆紙，強調了自己只是依附在對方世界中的裝飾，沒有獨立的空間和價值。"},"source":{"title":"牆紙","artists":["容祖兒"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_738","prev_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5a6556WW5YS__NzM4_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
